 dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Funny satirical packaging for BLEB detergent with collectible cards hidden inside.</span><br><span>Washing machine character looks mischievous, goofy smile, spinning eyes, tongue out.</span><br><span>Cards inside have absurd characters (cats, aliens, socks running away).</span><br><span>Style: bold meme aesthetic + glossy 3D product box.</span><br><span>Vivid neon colors, thick outlines, chaotic comic energy, dynamic pose.</span><br><span>Perfect for social media virality.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
