b2dbdcc888d03337239cf59e75.jpg" style="object-position: 0% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for E-Commerce Landing Page(Hero Section) (2) | Images :: Behance"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/fs/a50a13168411771.644ea2a6b2810.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/a50a13168411771.644ea2a6b2810.jpg" style="object-position: 100% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div></div>
<h3 data-start="2099" data-end="2133"><strong data-start="2103" data-end="2131">FULL LANDING PAGE PROMPT</strong></h3>
<p data-start="2134" data-end="2177">Vlož do Framer AI / Vercel AI / Webflow AI:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2179" data-end="3764"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Create a playful, high-converting landing page for the BLEB brand (Because Laundry Entertains Better).</span><br><br><span>Brand concept:</span><br><span>BLEB is a funny detergent that contains collectible cards inside each package. </span><br><span>The product is a mix of humor, surprise, and community fun. Target group: people who like memes, surprises, funny gifts, and quirky products.</span><br><br><span>Landing Page Structure:</span><br><br><span>1) HERO SECTION</span><br><span>- Large 3D render of the detergent box with spinning washing machine mascot.</span><br><span>- Short powerful headline:</span><br><span>  "BLEB – Laundry Just Got Entertaining"</span><br><span>- Subheadline:</span><br><span>  "Collect funny cards hidden in every detergent box."</span><br><span>- Animated washing machine drum (loop) on the right.</span><br><span>- CTA buttons:</span><br><span>  “Buy BLEB”</span><br><span>  “See Cards”</span><br><br><span>2) HOW IT WORKS</span><br><span>- Step boxes:</span><br><span>  1. “Open the BLEB box”</span><br><span>  2. “Find your surprise card”</span><br><span>  3. “Collect, trade, have fun”</span><br><br><span>3) PRODUCT GALLERY</span><br><span>- 3D renders of the detergent</span><br><span>- Close-ups of cards</span><br><span>- Packshot on white background</span><br><br><span>4) STORY / BRAND SECTION</span><br><span>- “Why BLEB exists?”</span><br><span>- Short fun text about making laundry less boring</span><br><br><span>5) SOCIAL PROOF</span><br><span>- Fake but funny reviews (“Finally detergent that doesn’t judge me.”)</span><br><br><span>6) COMMUNITY CALL TO ACTION</span><br><span>- Join BLEB Club</span><br><span>- Email form</span><br><span>- Icons of upcoming series of cards</span><br><br><span>7) FOOTER</span><br><span>- Minimalistic</span><br><span>- Links: About, Cards, Shop, Contact</span><br><span>- Copyright BLEB 2026</span><br><br><span>Design Style:</span><br><span>- Fun, bold, bright colors, meme energy</span><br><span>- Slight 3D feel, rounded sections, smooth animations</span><br><span>- Clean typography (Inter / Poppins)</span><br><span>- Big buttons, mobile-first</span><br><br><span>Make the page fully responsive.</span><br><span>Use modern animations and micro-interactions (hover effects, spinning drum, floating cards).</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3766" data-end="3769">
<h1 data-start="3771" data-end="3802">🔥 Pokud chceš — vytvořím ti:</h1>
<p data-start="3804" data-end="4022">✅ <strong data-start="3806" data-end="3844">kompletní hotový text pro celý web</strong><br data-start="3844" data-end="3847">
✅ <strong data-start="3849" data-end="3872">názvy edic kartiček</strong><br data-start="3872" data-end="3875">
✅ <strong data-start="3877" data-end="3894">úvodní slogan</strong><br data-start="3894" data-end="3897">
✅ <strong data-start="3899" data-end="3918">popisy produktů</strong><br data-start="3918" data-end="3921">
✅ <strong data-start="3923" data-end="3959">kompletní vizuální identitu BLEB</strong><br data-start="3959" data-end="3962">
✅ <strong data-start="3964" data-end="4022">návod jak to dát na Vercel (polopatě jako pro “blbce”)</strong></p>
<p data-start="4024" data-end="4115" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Chceš pokračovat? Pošli, jaký styl branding chceš (funny / premium / meme / cartoon / eco).</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Ba