sk-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="b9e211c6-8470-4606-b3c0-16a1553a0a23" data-testid="conversation-turn-6" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b9e211c6-8470-4606-b3c0-16a1553a0a23" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="308">Ano — <strong data-start="6" data-end="20">umím obojí</strong>:<br data-start="21" data-end="24">
👉 <strong data-start="27" data-end="57">vytvořit kompletní grafiku</strong> (hero image, logo, produktové rendery, ilustrace)<br data-start="107" data-end="110">
👉 <strong data-start="113" data-end="137">navrhnout i celý web</strong> (layout, texty, struktura)<br data-start="164" data-end="167">
👉 <strong data-start="170" data-end="261">a dokonce ti můžu rovnou vygenerovat hotový HTML/React/Framer/Starlight/Next.js projekt</strong>, který jen nahraješ na Vercel nebo Websupport.</p>
<p data-start="310" data-end="445">A podle toho, co děláš (BLEB / funny prací prášek + kartičky), ti umím vyrobit <strong data-start="389" data-end="397">styl</strong>, <strong data-start="399" data-end="409">vizuál</strong>, <strong data-start="411" data-end="420">obsah</strong>, i <strong data-start="424" data-end="444">technické řešení</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="447" data-end="450">
<h1 data-start="452" data-end="492">🔥 POTŘEBUJU OD TEBE 3 KRÁTKÉ ODPOVĚDI</h1>
<p data-start="493" data-end="553">Abych začala dělat grafiku a web přesně podle tvé představy:</p>
<h3 data-start="555" data-end="590">1) <strong data-start="562" data-end="590">Jaký styl grafiky chceš?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="591" data-end="599">Vyber 1:</p>
<ol data-start="601" data-end="853">
<li data-start="601" data-end="662">
<p data-start="604" data-end="662"><strong data-start="604" data-end="620">Funny + meme</strong> (šílená pračka, vtipné kartičky, chaos)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="663" data-end="720">
<p data-start="666" data-end="720"><strong data-start="666" data-end="683">3D Pixar styl</strong> (roztomilá pračka jako postavička)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="721" data-end="773">
<p data-start="724" data-end="773"><strong data-start="724" data-end="747">Premium / Apple eco</strong> (minimal, čisté balení)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="774" data-end="803">
<p data-start="777" data-end="803"><strong data-start="777" data-end="801">Retro 90’s detergent</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="804" data-end="828">
<p data-start="807" data-end="828"><strong data-start="807" data-end="826">Anime / cartoon</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="829" data-end="853">
<p data-start="832" data-end="853"><strong data-start="832" data-end="853">Jiný — napiš jaký</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="855" data-end="858">
<h3 data-start="860" data-end="914">2) <strong data-start="867" data-end="914">Co přesně bude hlavní grafika v hero sekci?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="915" data-end="925">Například:</p>
<ul data-start="927" data-end="1055">
<li data-start="927" data-end="960">
<p data-start="929" data-end="960">3D balení pracího prášku BLEB</p>
</li>
<li data-start="961" data-end="988">
<p data-start="963" data-end="988">pračka s točícím bubnem</p>
</li>
<li data-start="989" data-end="1019">
<p data-start="991" data-end="1019">kartičky létající z prášku</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1020" data-end="1035">
<p data-start="1022" data-end="1035">kombo všeho</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1036" data-end="1055">
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1055">nebo něco jiného?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1057" data-end="1060">
<h3 data-start="1062" data-end="1117">3) <strong data-start="1069" data-end="1117">Chceš, abych ti rovnou vytvořila i celý web?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1124">Vyber:</p>
<ul data-start="1126" data-end="1362">
<li data-start="1126" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1128" data-end="1171"><strong data-start="1128" data-end="1169">Ano, FRAMER (nejrychlejší a nejhezčí)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1215">
<p data-start="1174" data-end="1215"><strong data-start="1174" data-end="1213">Ano, Webflow (profi, hezká animace)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1216" data-end="1246">
<p data-start="1218" data-end="1246"><strong data-start="1218" data-end="1244">Ano, čistý HTML/CSS/JS</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1247" data-end="1286">
<p data-start="1249" data-end="1286"><strong data-start="1249" data-end="1284">Ano, Next.js projekt pro Vercel</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1287" data-end="1340">
<p data-start="1289" data-end="1340"><strong data-start="1289" data-end="1338">Ano, jednoduchý Websupport hosting (PHP/HTML)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1341" data-end="1362">
<p data-start="1343" data-end="1362"><strong data-start="1343" data-end="1362">Ne, jen grafiku</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1364" data-end="1367">
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1395">💬 Stačí odpovědět stylem:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1397" data-end="1468">
<ol data-start="1399" data-end="1468">
<li data-start="1399" data-end="1412">
<p data-start="1402" data-end="1412">3D Pixar</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1415" data-end="1446">
<p data-start="1418" data-end="1446">Balení + pračka + kartičky</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1449" data-end="1468">
<p data-start="1452" data-end="1468">Next.js + Vercel</p>
</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1470" data-end="1554" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">A já okamžitě začnu tvořit — grafiku ti vyrobím a web ti postavím přesně podle toho.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad respo