 doména, až zítra - udělám si přístup do gib hubu a Vercel už máme - chci landing page - bude tam ta moje pračka  s videama - než to navrhneš řekni mi co dál</div></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary my-2 me-4 flex flex-row justify-end gap-1 text-xs"></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="2c6063ed-4625-4220-be47-c7729a8e7530" data-testid="conversation-turn-8" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2c6063ed-4625-4220-be47-c7729a8e7530" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="106">Perfektní — <strong data-start="12" data-end="85">jsi přesně ve fázi, kdy můžeme reálně začít stavět celou landing page</strong>.<br data-start="86" data-end="89">
A protože už máš:</p>
<ul data-start="108" data-end="286">
<li data-start="108" data-end="176">
<p data-start="110" data-end="176">✔️ <strong data-start="113" data-end="129">pračka fotka</strong> (budeme z ní dělat hero grafiku + 3D efekty)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="177" data-end="194">
<p data-start="179" data-end="194">✔️ <strong data-start="182" data-end="192">Vercel</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="195" data-end="222">
<p data-start="197" data-end="222">✔️ <strong data-start="200" data-end="220">budeš mít GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="223" data-end="286">
<p data-start="225" data-end="286">✔️ <strong data-start="228" data-end="264">doména washerlife.com je koupená</strong> (DNS přidáme zítra)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="288" data-end="330">…tak teď je správný čas nastavit workflow.</p>
<hr data-start="332" data-end="335">
<h1 data-start="337" data-end="392">✅ CO POTŘEBUJU OD TEBE <strong data-start="362" data-end="369">TEĎ</strong> (než začnu tvořit web)</h1>
<p data-start="393" data-end="449">Abych ti mohla dodat <em data-start="414" data-end="430">hotový projekt</em>, potřebuji 4 věci:</p>
<hr data-start="451" data-end="454">
<h2 data-start="456" data-end="508"><strong data-start="459" data-end="506">1) Vyber styl webu (základní vizuální směr)</strong></h2>
<p data-start="509" data-end="563">Vyber 1 a já podle toho navrhnu celý design + grafiku:</p>
<h3 data-start="565" data-end="652"><strong data-start="569" data-end="625">A) Loundry styl (mlha, atmosféra, poetická estetika)</strong> – jako na prvním obrázku</h3>
<p data-start="653" data-end="671">— „umění + práčka“</p>
<h3 data-start="673" data-end="730"><strong data-start="677" data-end="728">B) Minimal / Apple look (čisté, bílé, prémiové)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="731" data-end="767">— fokus na pračku, produkt, eleganci</p>
<h3 data-start="769" data-end="808"><strong data-start="773" data-end="806">C) Surreal / creepy aesthetic</strong></h3>
<p data-start="809" data-end="867">— opuštěné nádraží, tajemné zprávy, „today’s wash message“</p>
<h3 data-start="869" data-end="910"><strong data-start="873" data-end="908">D) Funny / meme / šílená pračka</strong></h3>
<p data-start="911" data-end="966">— ale podle fotky bych šla spíš do seriózního stylu A/B</p>
<p data-start="968" data-end="1007">Napiš jen písmeno a já to celé navrhnu.</p>
<hr data-start="1009" data-end="1012">
<h2 data-start="1014" data-end="1056"><strong data-start="1017" data-end="1054">2) Jaký má být obsah na homepage?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1057" data-end="1073">Potřebuji vědět:</p>
<h3 data-start="1075" data-end="1113"><strong data-start="1079" data-end="1111">Budeš tam dávat denní video?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1114" data-end="1171">(Loundry má „today’s wash message“ + video pračky/koláže)</p>
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1179">Vyber:</p>
<ul data-start="1181" data-end="1268">
<li data-start="1181" data-end="1213">
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1213"><strong data-start="1183" data-end="1211">Ano – denní video pračky</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1214" data-end="1247">
<p data-start="1216" data-end="1247"><strong data-start="1216" data-end="1245">Ano – video ale jen občas</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1248" data-end="1268">
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1268"><strong data-start="1250" data-end="1268">Ne – bez videa</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1270" data-end="1273">
<h2 data-start="1275" data-end="1317"><strong data-start="1278" data-end="1317">3) Má tam být „message of the day“?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1318" data-end="1330">Jak Loundry:</p>
<ul data-start="1332" data-end="1385">
<li data-start="1332" data-end="1358">
<p data-start="1334" data-end="1358">“Time turns every tide.”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1359" data-end="1385">
<p data-start="1361" data-end="1385">“Memories are cyclical.”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1387" data-end="1471">Chceš taky <strong data-start="1398" data-end="1422">jednu větu každý den</strong>?<br data-start="1423" data-end="1426">
→ můžeme dělat automatické generování quotes.</p>
<hr data-start="1473" data-end="1476">
<h2 data-start="1478" data-end="1520"><strong data-start="1481" data-end="1520">4) Chceš e-shop hned, nebo později?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1521" data-end="1536">Budeš prodávat:</p>
<ul data-start="1538" data-end="1581">
<li data-start="1538" data-end="1549">
<p data-start="1540" data-end="1549">prášek?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1550" data-end="1563">
<p data-start="1552" data-end="1563">kartičky?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1564" data-end="1581">
<p data-start="1566" data-end="1581">merch (BLEB)?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1583" data-end="1589">Vyber:</p>
<ul data-start="1591" data-end="1688">
<li data-start="1591" data-end="1629">
<p data-start="1593" data-end="1629"><strong data-start="1593" data-end="1627">Teď hned jednoduchý BUY button</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1630" data-end="1658">
<p data-start="1632" data-end="1658"><strong data-start="1632" data-end="1656">Později (jen teaser)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1659" data-end="1688">
<p data-start="1661" data-end="1688"><strong data-start="1661" data-end="1688">Nikdy (jen art projekt)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1690" data-end="1693">
<h1 data-start="1695" data-end="1727">🔥 Až mi tohle pošleš, udělám:</h1>
<h3 data-start="1729" data-end="1759">✔️ hotový design (návrh)</h3>
<h3 data-start="1760" data-end="1826">✔️ navrženou hero grafiku s tvojí pračkou (ve stylu A/B/C/D)</h3>
<h3 data-start="1827" data-end="1878">✔️ kompletní landing page k nahrání na Vercel</h3>
<h3 data-start="1879" data-end="1942">✔️ strukturu GitHub repa (Next.js 14 / Tailwind / Motion)</h3>
<h3 data-start="1943" data-end="2011">✔️ instructions pro DNS → Websupport → Vercel → washerlife.com</h3>
<hr data-start="2013" data-end="2016">
<h1 data-start="2018" data-end="2054">💡 IDEÁLNÍ KRÁTKÁ ODPOVĚĎ OD TEBE:</h1>
<blockquote data-start="2056" data-end="2160">
<ol data-start="2058" data-end="2160">
<li data-start="2058" data-end="2079">
<p data-start="2061" data-end="2079">A – Loundry styl</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2082" data-end="2104">
<p data-start="2085" data-end="2104">Ano – denní video</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2107" data-end="2136">
<p data-start="2110" data-end="2136">Ano – message of the day</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2139" data-end="2160">
<p data-start="2142" data-end="2160">Teď jen BUY button</p>
</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2162" data-end="2209" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Jakmile mi to pošleš → začnu <em data-start="2191" data-end="2201">okamžitě</em> tvořit.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad r