<p data-start="472" data-end="498">(Moje doporučení pro tebe)</p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Laundry Aesthetic"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://i.pinimg.com/236x/0f/99/ee/0f99eeb9fe5a25dc441e549a99a55a5d.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/0f99eeb9fe5a25dc441e549a99a55a5d.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 98%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for liminal space Washing machine by snivez -- Fur Affinity [dot] net"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://d.furaffinity.net/art/snivez/1639340707/1639340707.snivez_liminalspace4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/ZzVs09nOhqvD7yEZiEeCYNq_c2Ww-YTm1WCWveyjoWVFZE2LWmxa1thtnnA9eH1O5TbNNwV471HYBAV_oZ32NpAcecHdzT6s4yaCYKMqHz5a6c5V9MdSWoqZzMcnvZGDbIWf2mnuw1tJzFyoC5p3rA" style="object-position: 50% 100%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Brain-washing Machines #5&#39; - Surreal Stencil Art – Contemporary Australian  Surrealism by Geoff Cunningham – Geoff Cunningham Art"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://geoffcunninghamart.com/cdn/shop/files/BrainWashingMachines_5_LR.jpg?v=1701296620" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/BrainWashingMachines_5_LR.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 0%; opacity: 1;"></div></button><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-2 bottom-2 z-20 flex max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)] flex-wrap items-end justify-end gap-1.5"><div class="shrink-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 text-white backdrop-blur-md backdrop-brightness-75"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#266724" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><span class="text-xs font-semibold">4</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="542" data-end="558">Vizuál bude mít:</p>
<ul data-start="560" data-end="728">
<li data-start="560" data-end="579">
<p data-start="562" data-end="579">jemnou <strong data-start="569" data-end="577">mlhu</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="580" data-end="625">
<p data-start="582" data-end="625">„liminal“ nádražní / průmyslovou estetiku</p>
</li>
<li data-start="626" data-end="646">
<p data-start="628" data-end="646">tichou atmosféru</p>
</li>
<li data-start="647" data-end="682">
<p data-start="649" data-end="682">pračku jako <strong data-start="661" data-end="680">mystický objekt</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="683" data-end="728">
<p data-start="685" data-end="728">světlo vycházející z bubnu (zlaté, teplé)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="730" data-end="792">Působí to draze, umělecky, unikátně a přesně do té tvé nálady.</p>
<hr data-start="794" data-end="797">
<h1 data-start="799" data-end="850">📸 1) <strong data-start="807" data-end="833">Grafika pro HERO sekci</strong> (obrázek nahoře)</h1>
<p data-start="851" data-end="871">Udělám z tvé pračky:</p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Front Load Washing Machine Isolated on White. Front View of White Freestanding Fully Automatic Top Loading Washer with Integrated Control Panel. Domestic Household Appliances. Home Innovation"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-3/le6c0MIaqy_5GsnKxXyACOyjkwfUQAVedqisZaiMtX7cHmBOMTa7I1CyyE2tlpLduHX0-6uFIuQxsYn7WaS70sw7UYZtCwMltLhqBQD_Ggo?purpose=fullsize&amp;v=1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/le6c0MIaqy_5GsnKxXyACOyjkwfUQAVedqisZaiMtX7cHmBOMTa7I1CyyE2tlpLduHX0-6uFIuQxsYn7WaS70sw7UYZtCwMltLhqBQD_Ggo" style="opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for High-Resolution Washing Machine Image Isolated On Clear Background For  Product Use PNG Images | PNG Free Download - Pikbest"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://img.pikbest.com/png-images/20241024/high-resolution-washing-machine-image-isolated-on-clear-background-for-product-use_10998610.png%21w700wp" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/high-resolution-washing-machine-image-isolated-on-clear-background-for-product-use_10998610.png!w700wp" style="object-position: 50% 55.6%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div></div>
<p data-start="915" data-end="927">Styl úpravy:</p>
<ul data-start="929" data-end="1177">
<li data-start="929" data-end="1008">
<p data-start="931" data-end="1008">tvůj <strong data-start="936" data-end="960">originální Panasonic</strong> zůstane → jen ho graficky posunu do atmosféry</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1009" data-end="1048">
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1048">buben bude <strong data-start="1022" data-end="1032">svítit</strong> (golden glow)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1049" data-end="1126">
<p data-start="1051" data-end="1126">pozadí = filmové, rozmazané, lehce strašidelné koleje / průmyslová plocha</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1127" data-end="1177">
<p data-start="1129" data-end="1177">jemný prach, teplo světla, minimalistický text</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1197"><strong data-start="1179" data-end="1197">Příklad sekce:</strong></p>
<p data-start="1199" data-end="1282"><strong data-start="1199" data-end="1213">WASHERLIFE</strong><br data-start="1213" data-end="1216">
<em data-start="1216" data-end="1255">Where the ordinary goes to disappear.</em><br data-start="1255" data-end="1258">
[ Watch Today’s Wash ]</p>
<hr data-start="1284" data-end="1287">
<h1 data-start="1289" data-end="1330">📹 2) <strong data-start="1297" data-end="1330">Sekce s videem (Today’s Wash)</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1342">Sem půjde:</p>
<ul data-start="1344" data-end="1452">
<li data-start="1344" data-end="1366">
<p data-start="1346" data-end="1366">tvoje video pračky</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1367" data-end="1395">
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1395">nebo video mlhy / kolejí</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1396" data-end="1452">
<p data-start="1398" data-end="1452">nebo mix obojího, kde pračka dělá „message of the day“</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1454" data-end="1509">Video bude s efektem <strong data-start="1475" data-end="1508">film grain + low contrast fog</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1511" data-end="1562">Působí to jako umělecký projekt (což přesně chceš).</p>
<hr data-start="1564" data-end="1567">
<h1 data-start="1569" data-end="1617">🧼 3) <strong data-start="1577" data-end="1617">Powder section (pokud chceš produkt)</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1619" data-end="1633">Design prášku:</p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for White plastic bag of laundry detergent - blank realistic mockup for product branding and packaging design."><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-3/p0P_B3cNqXwWVCeadzwQxXN8id3ZVqKGXXg05W1SlNNPkuK2ramPWSbKCwNEotCD8xQyq2SM2G7F0qizf6-a-iyPlovs9rE8bbgrcn0xdz8?purpose=fullsize&amp;v=1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/p0P_B3cNqXwWVCeadzwQxXN8id3ZVqKGXXg05W1SlNNPkuK2ramPWSbKCwNEotCD8xQyq2SM2G7F0qizf6-a-iyPlovs9rE8bbgrcn0xdz8" style="opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for model package design for products| how to make your own package"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/06/a2/7e/06a27e2203337e4303dc2247dcbf5669.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/06a27e2203337e4303dc2247dcbf5669.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 33.3%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div></div>
<p data-start="1677" data-end="1685">Bude to:</p>
<ul data-start="1687" data-end="1834">
<li data-start="1687" data-end="1714">
<p data-start="1689" data-end="1714">čisté, bílé / pastelové</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1715" data-end="1755">
<p data-start="1717" data-end="1755">s textem „White Wash“ + „Color Wash“</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1756" data-end="1785">
<p data-start="1758" data-end="1785">bez loga → jen typografie</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1786" data-end="1834">
<p data-start="1788" data-end="1834">poetický vibe: <em data-start="1803" data-end="1832">Different story. Same wash.</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1836" data-end="1839">
<h1 data-start="1841" data-end="1870">📝 4) <strong data-start="1849" data-end="1870">Typografie a text</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1871" data-end="1889">Navrhnu kombinaci:</p>
<ul data-start="1891" data-end="1975">
<li data-start="1891" data-end="1932">
<p data-start="1893" data-end="1932"><strong data-start="1893" data-end="1910">Serif (title)</strong> – vysoký, elegantní</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1933" data-end="1975">
<p data-start="1935" data-end="1975"><strong data-start="1935" data-end="1956">Sans-serif (body)</strong> – čistý, moderní</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1977" data-end="1989">Texty budou:</p>
<ul data-start="1991" data-end="2103">
<li data-start="1991" data-end="2001">
<p data-start="1993" data-end="2001">krátké</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2002" data-end="2014">
<p data-start="2004" data-end="2014">poetické</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2015" data-end="2026">
<p data-start="2017" data-end="2026">filmové</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2027" data-end="2103">
<p data-start="2029" data-end="2103">přesně jako vibe „imagine you’re watching your memories being washed away“</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2105" data-end="2108">
<h1 data-start="2110" data-end="2161">🧱 5) <strong data-start="2118" data-end="2161">Struktura Landing Page (co ti postavím)</strong></h1>
<ol data-start="2163" data-end="2550">
<li data-start="2163" data-end="2272">
<p data-start="2166" data-end="2272"><strong data-start="2166" data-end="2182">Hero Section</strong><br data-start="2182" data-end="2185">
– pračka v mlze<br data-start="2203" data-end="2206">
– headline + message of the day<br data-start="2240" data-end="2243">
– CTA „Watch Today’s Wash“</p>
