<li data-start="143" data-end="211">
<p data-start="145" data-end="211">ale pořád <strong data-start="155" data-end="172">cine-art styl</strong>, aby to působilo geniálně a ne lacině.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="213" data-end="299">Teď ti ukážu přesný <strong data-start="233" data-end="259">návrh vizuální grafiky</strong>, který potom převedeme na landing page.</p>
<hr data-start="301" data-end="304">
<h1 data-start="306" data-end="353">🎨 <strong data-start="311" data-end="351">NÁVRH TVÉ HERO GRAFIKY — WASHER LIFE</strong></h1>
<p data-start="354" data-end="396">(inspirace Loundry, ale humor + meme vibe)</p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Aesthetic Washing Machine"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/b1/0f/87/b10f875a9b8ed858c56e8fc292ba3b73.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/b10f875a9b8ed858c56e8fc292ba3b73.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 66.1%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Art-Poster - Astronaut Doing Laundry - Baard Martinussen"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://www.walleditions.com/29708-large_default/art-poster-astronaut-doing-laundry-baard-martinussen.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/art-poster-astronaut-doing-laundry-baard-martinussen.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 12.3%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative 