<h3 data-start="440" data-end="467"><strong data-start="444" data-end="467">Koncept hero sekce:</strong></h3>
<p data-start="469" data-end="582"><strong data-start="469" data-end="484">WASHER LIFE</strong><br data-start="484" data-end="487">
<em data-start="487" data-end="512">Where cycles never end.</em><br data-start="512" data-end="515">
<em data-start="515" data-end="539">Where socks disappear.</em><br data-start="539" data-end="542">
<em data-start="542" data-end="580">Where your sanity hangs by a thread.</em></p>
<p data-start="584" data-end="609">Uprostřed <strong data-start="594" data-end="608">tvá pračka</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="611" data-end="824">
<li data-start="611" data-end="672">
<p data-start="613" data-end="672">buben <strong data-start="619" data-end="634">zlatě svítí</strong> (světlo života / teplo / tajemství)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="673" data-end="729">
<p data-start="675" data-end="729">kolem ní <strong data-start="684" data-end="692">mlha</strong>, lehký „railway + industrial“ vibe</p>
</li>
<li data-start="730" data-end="792">
<p data-start="732" data-end="792">pračka je <strong data-start="742" data-end="761">mírně front-lit</strong>, pozadí uplně cinematic blur</p>
</li>
<li data-start="793" data-end="824">
<p data-start="795" data-end="824">nahoře humor, dole elegance</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="826" data-end="926"><strong data-start="826" data-end="874">Meme pocit → „This machine has seen things.“</strong><br data-start="874" data-end="877">
<strong data-start="877" data-end="926">Cinematic umění → aby to nepůsobilo kýčovitě.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="928" data-end="931">
<h1 data-start="933" data-end="984">🧩 <strong data-start="938" data-end="984">Co bude v HERO vizuálu (přesná kompozice):</strong></h1>
<ol data-start="986" data-end="1475">
<li data-start="986" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="989" data-end="1001"><strong data-start="989" data-end="999">Pozadí</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1005" data-end="1099">
<li data-start="1005" data-end="1033">
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1033">železniční koleje v mlze</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1037" data-end="1053">
<p data-start="1039" data-end="1053">low contrast</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1057" data-end="1071">
<p data-start="1059" data-end="1071">soft grain</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1075" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="1077" data-end="1099">utopené světlo v dálce</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1101" data-end="1230">
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1133"><strong data-start="1104" data-end="1118">Tvá pračka</strong> (ta z fotky)</p>
<ul data-start="1137" data-end="1230">
<li data-start="1137" data-end="1167">
<p data-start="1139" data-end="1167">vyretušovaná → čisté hrany</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1171" data-end="1198">
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1198">buben glowing warm gold</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1202" data-end="1230">
<p data-start="1204" data-end="1230">jemné odlesky, čisté stíny</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1232" data-end="1372">
<p data-start="1235" data-end="1248"><strong data-start="1235" data-end="1246">Nadpisy</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1252" data-end="1372">
<li data-start="1252" data-end="1291">
<p data-start="1254" data-end="1291">WASHER LIFE (serif font, elegantní)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1295" data-end="1322">
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1322">Where cycles never end.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1326" data-end="1372">
<p data-start="1328" data-end="1372">Daily wash message: „Something died inside.“</p>
</li>
</ul>
