<hr data-start="446" data-end="449">
<h1 data-start="451" data-end="514">🎨 <strong data-start="456" data-end="514">NÁVRH HERO GRAFIKY — WASHER LIFE (Cine + Meme Edition)</strong></h1>
<h2 data-start="516" data-end="526">⭐ Název</h2>
<p data-start="527" data-end="542"><strong data-start="527" data-end="542">WASHER LIFE</strong></p>
<p data-start="544" data-end="633">Typografie = vysoký serif (Garamond / Cormorant / Playfair)<br data-start="603" data-end="606">
→ elegantní, téměř luxusní.</p>
<h2 data-start="635" data-end="649">⭐ Podnadpis</h2>
<p data-start="650" data-end="684"><strong data-start="650" data-end="684">Where normality goes to rinse.</strong></p>
<h2 data-start="686" data-end="719">⭐ Tvoje pračka (hlavní objekt)</h2>
<ul data-start="720" data-end="879">
