<p data-start="607" data-end="623">Inspirace stylu:</p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for A foggy train station with a train on the tracks photo – Free City Image on  Unsplash"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1654608053920-7a08eddabeaf?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=jpg&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&amp;ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;q=60&amp;w=3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/photo-1654608053920-7a08eddabeaf" style="object-position: 50% 0%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for FOG (2) | Images :: Behance"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://mir-s3-cdn-cf.behance.net/project_modules/fs/4c958c69509035.5b842e6f5c497.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/4c958c69509035.5b842e6f5c497.jpg" style="object-position: 0% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Underworld"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/00/7b/af/007baf0b3b7b94c7d964dfa8eb9fa2d4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/007baf0b3b7b94c7d964dfa8eb9fa2d4.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 31.7%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="667" data-end="670">
<h3 data-start="672" data-end="733">🎬 <strong data-start="679" data-end="733">B) Po hero grafice udělám design celé landing page</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="734" data-end="907">
<li data-start="734" data-end="764">
<p data-start="736" data-end="764">Today’s Wash (video sekce)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="765" data-end="800">
<p data-start="767" data-end="800">Product sekce (meme detergenty)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="801" data-end="815">
<p data-start="803" data-end="815">Why? sekce</p>
</li>
<li data-start="816" data-end="826">
<p data-start="818" data-end="826">Footer</p>
</li>
<li data-start="827" data-end="878">
<p data-start="829" data-end="878">layout identický vibe jako Loundry, ale humorný</p>
</li>
<li data-start="879" data-end="907">
<p data-start="881" data-end="907">texty v „cine + meme“ modu</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="909" data-end="912">
<h3 data-start="914" data-end="963">💻 <strong data-start="921" data-end="963">C) Nakóduju Next.js + Tailwind projekt</strong></h3>
<p data-start="964" data-end="993">Přesně připravený pro Vercel:</p>
<ul data-start="995" data-end="1229">
<li data-start="995" data-end="1032">
<p data-start="997" data-end="1032"><code data-start="997" data-end="1015">/pages/index.tsx</code> – landing page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1033" data-end="1080">
<p data-start="1035" data-end="1080"><code data-start="1035" data-end="1053">/public/hero.png</code> – tvoje pračka cinematic</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1081" data-end="1115">
<p data-start="1083" data-end="1115"><code data-start="1083" data-end="1113">/components/MessageOfDay.tsx</code></p>
</li>
