<p data-start="134" data-end="290">Použiji <strong data-start="142" data-end="166">tvoji pračku z fotky</strong>, jen ji zasadím do cine+meal prostředí (mlha + koleje + glow).<br data-start="229" data-end="232">
Níže máš <strong data-start="241" data-end="268">přesný vizuální nástřel</strong>, jak to bude působit.</p>
<hr data-start="292" data-end="295">
<h1 data-start="297" data-end="343">🎨 <strong data-start="302" data-end="341">WASHER LIFE — HERO VIZUÁL (KONCEPT)</strong></h1>
<p data-start="344" data-end="370"><em data-start="344" data-end="370">50% cinematic / 50% meme</em></p>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for A History of Trains in Film &amp; Television | Avanti West Coast"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://www.avantiwestcoast.co.uk/-/media/rail-200/train-culture/trains-in-film/trains-in-fog.jpg?h=400&amp;w=600" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/trains in fog.jpg" style="object-position: 100% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Brain-washing Machines #5&#39; - Surreal Stencil Art – Contemporary Australian  Surrealism by Geoff Cunningham – Geoff Cunningham Art"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://geoffcunninghamart.com/cdn/shop/files/BrainWashingMachines_5_LR.jpg?v=1701296620" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/BrainWashingMachines_5_LR.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 0%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for 40 Pics Of Slightly Unsettling “Liminal Spaces”"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/95/32/8c/95328c90e959a05e8aed6255e3809b37.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./Grafika a landing page_files/95328c90e959a05e8aed6255e3809b37.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 99.6%; opacity: 1;"></div></button><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-2 bottom-2 z-20 flex max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)] flex-wrap items-end justify-end gap-1.5"><div class="shrink-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 text-white backdrop-blur-md backdrop-brightness-75"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#266724" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><span class="text-xs font-semibold">4</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="414" data-end="417">
<h1 data-start="419" data-end="472">🖼️ <strong data-start="425" data-end="472">Jak bude vypadat tvoje pračka v hero sekci:</strong></h1>
<h3 data-start="474" data-end="513">✔️ Tvoje pračka = střed kompozice</h3>
<ul data-start="514" data-end="614">
<li data-start="514" data-end="533">
<p data-start="516" data-end="533">čistě vyříznutá</p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="552">
<p data-start="536" data-end="552">lehce zvětšená</p>
</li>
<li data-start="553" data-end="594">
<p data-start="555" data-end="594">mírný „hero angle“ perspektivní efekt</p>
</li>
<li data-start="595" data-end="614">
<p data-start="597" data-end="614">bez tvrdých stínů</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="616" data-end="660">✔️ Buben bude svítit teple (jen lehce)</h3>
<p data-start="661" data-end="761"><strong data-start="661" data-end="701">Glow: jemné teplé světlo (cinematic)</strong><br data-start="701" data-end="704">
→ zvýrazní to „duši pračky“, ale bude to pořád elegantní.</p>
<h3 data-start="763" data-end="802">✔️ Pozadí = filmový „fog railway“</h3>
<ul data-start="803" data-end="968">
<li data-start="803" data-end="831">
<p data-start="805" data-end="831">železniční koleje v mlze</p>
</li>
<li data-start="832" data-end="850">
