<p data-start="1379" data-end="1453">Pozadí jako na vzorku → jemná textura papíru, vysušené kvítí, měkké stíny.</p>
<hr data-start="1455" data-end="1458">
<h1 data-start="1460" data-end="1506">🧩 <strong data-start="1465" data-end="1506">4) LORE / STORY SECTION (cine + meme)</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1508" data-end="1538">Na levé straně připnutý papír:</p>
<p data-start="1540" data-end="1688"><strong data-start="1540" data-end="1594">There used to be a laundromat near the old tracks.</strong><br data-start="1594" data-end="1597">
People said strange things happened there.<br data-start="1639" data-end="1642">
Some still do.<br data-start="1656" data-end="1659">
<em data-start="1659" data-end="1688">We just decided to film it.</em></p>
<p data-start="1690" data-end="1750">Vpravo vložená fotografie staré prádelny / baru (cinematic).</p>
<hr data-start="1752" data-end="1755">
