g">&lt;a</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">href</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"#buy"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"btn btn-outline"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><span>BUY</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;p</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"subtitle"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><span>Same powder. Different trauma.</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ6">&lt;!-- STORY / LORE --&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"section section-paper"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">id</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"story"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"container story-grid"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"paper paper-story"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;p&gt;</span><br><span>            There used to be a laundromat near the old tracks.</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>            People said strange things happened there.</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>            Some still do. We just decided to film it.</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>        </