sed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="68080626-e04c-4b16-902c-805213ee1b2b" data-testid="conversation-turn-36" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="560c45dd-82aa-4d9a-a5c1-df8cd62bd38a" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="85">Super — jsme ve velmi dobré fázi.<br data-start="33" data-end="36">
👉 <strong data-start="39" data-end="83">Návrh máš. Kód máš. Postup nasazení máš.</strong></p>
<p data-start="87" data-end="129">Teď můžeš udělat další krok kdykoli chceš:</p>
<hr data-start="131" data-end="134">
<h1 data-start="136" data-end="169">✔️ CO JE AKTUÁLNÍ TODO PRO TEBE</h1>
<p data-start="170" data-end="198">(v krátké, přehledné podobě)</p>
<h3 data-start="200" data-end="240"><strong data-start="204" data-end="240">1) Vytvořit složku <code data-start="225" data-end="238">washerlife/</code></strong></h3>
<p data-start="241" data-end="251">Do ní dej:</p>
<ul data-start="253" data-end="383">
<li data-start="253" data-end="267">
<p data-start="255" data-end="267"><code data-start="255" data-end="267">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="268" data-end="282">
<p data-start="270" data-end="282"><code data-start="270" data-end="282">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="283" data-end="383">
<p data-start="285" data-end="383"><code data-start="285" data-end="306">washerlife-hero.jpg</code> (zatím použij ten koncept z Dreamu, později vyměníme za tvoji finální fotku)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="385" data-end="415"><strong data-start="389" data-end="415">2) Nahrát to na GitHub</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="416" data-end="474">
<li data-start="416" data-end="450">
<p data-start="418" data-end="450">GitHub → New Repo → <code data-start="438" data-end="450">washerlife</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="451" data-end="474">
<p data-start="453" data-end="474">Upload files → commit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="476" data-end="511"><strong data-start="480" data-end="511">3) Připojit repo ve Vercelu</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="512" data-end="579">
<li data-start="512" data-end="557">
<p data-start="514" data-end="557">Vercel → New Project → vybrat repo → Deploy</p>
</li>
<li data-start="558" data-end="579">
<p data-start="560" data-end="579">Hotovo do 10 vteřin</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="581" data-end="628"><strong data-start="585" data-end="628">4) Zítra přidáš doménu <code data-start="610" data-end="626">washerlife.com</code></strong></h3>
<ul data-start="629" data-end="705">
<li data-start="629" data-end="663">
<p data-start="631" data-end="663">Vercel → Project → Domains → Add</p>
</li>
<li data-start="664" data-end="705">
<p data-start="666" data-end="705">Websupport → DNS → nasměrovat na Vercel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="707" data-end="750"><strong data-start="707" data-end="750">Po 15–60 minutách poběží veřejná verze.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="752" data-end="755">
<h1 data-start="757" data-end="794">✔️ CO UDĚLÁM JÁ, AŽ BUDEŠ CHTÍT DÁL</h1>
<p data-start="796" data-end="804">Jakmile:</p>
<ul data-start="806" data-end="892">
<li data-start="806" data-end="825">
<p data-start="808" data-end="825">přidáš hero fotku</p>
</li>
<li data-start="826" data-end="850">
<p data-start="828" data-end="850">budeš mít video pračky</p>
</li>
<li data-start="851" data-end="892">
<p data-start="853" data-end="892">budeš chtít vyladit text nebo atmosféru</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="894" data-end="902">→ já ti:</p>
<h3 data-start="904" data-end="965"><strong data-start="908" data-end="963">1) Upravím finální design podle reálné fotky pračky</strong></h3>
<p data-start="966" data-end="1011">(žádný concept art – skutečný cinematic shot)</p>
<h3 data-start="1013" data-end="1061"><strong data-start="1017" data-end="1061">2) Přidám sekci s reálným videem (embed)</strong></h3>
<h3 data-start="1063" data-end="1119"><strong data-start="1067" data-end="1119">3) Vylepším CTA, mikroanimace, efekty, plynulost</strong></h3>
<h3 data-start="1121" data-end="1202"><strong data-start="1125" data-end="1202">4) Udělám verzi s headless CMS, aby sis mohl měnit texty i video bez kódu</strong></h3>
<h3 data-start="1204" data-end="1272"><strong data-start="1208" data-end="1270">5) Pokud budeš chtít, udělám mini e-shop (Stripe / PayPal)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1273" data-end="1311">→ BUY tlačítka začnou reálně fungovat.</p>
<hr data-start="1313" data-end="1316">
<h1 data-start="1318" data-end="1357">✔️ Pokud chceš, můžu ti teď vytvořit:</h1>
<ul data-start="1358" data-end="1576">
<li data-start="1358" data-end="1403">
<p data-start="1360" data-end="1403"><strong data-start="1360" data-end="1371">favicon</strong> (W, buben pračky, zlatý glow)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1404" data-end="1453">
<p data-start="1406" data-end="1453"><strong data-start="1406" data-end="1428">logo „WASHER LIFE“</strong> v elegantní typografii</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1454" data-end="1494">
<p data-start="1456" data-end="1494"><strong data-start="1456" data-end="1492">social preview image (OpenGraph)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1495" data-end="1527">
<p data-start="1497" data-end="1527"><strong data-start="1497" data-end="1516">verzi pro mobil</strong> (mockup)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1528" data-end="1576">
<p data-start="1530" data-end="1576"><strong data-start="1530" data-end="1576">e-mail template pro „<a data-start="1553" data-end="1573" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">order@washerlife.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a>“</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1578" data-end="1689">Stačí napsat:<br data-start="1591" data-end="1594">
<strong data-start="1594" data-end="1612">„Chci favicon“</strong> nebo <strong data-start="1618" data-end="1633">„Chci logo“</strong> nebo <strong data-start="1639" data-end="1658">„Chci OG image“</strong> nebo <strong data-start="1664" data-end="1688">„Chci mobilní verzi“</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1691" data-end="1704">A uděláme to.</p>
<hr data-start="1706" data-end="1709">
<p data-start="1711" data-end="1793" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Až budeš na GitHubu / Vercelu, klidně mi hoď link → zkontroluju, upravím, doladím.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad respons