Bez programování, bez terminálu, bez komplikací.<br data-start="91" data-end="94">
Uložíš to stejně jako normální text, jen to bude mít koncovku <strong data-start="156" data-end="165">.html</strong> a <strong data-start="168" data-end="176">.css</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="179" data-end="238">Použijeme aplikaci, kterou máš ve všech Linux distribucích:</p>
<h3 data-start="240" data-end="313"><strong data-start="244" data-end="311">🟢 GNOME Text Editor / Gedit / Kate / Mousepad (podle desktopu)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="314" data-end="359">Je to normální poznámkový blok → to zvládneš.</p>
<hr data-start="361" data-end="364">
<h1 data-start="366" data-end="433">🧩 <strong data-start="371" data-end="433">1) Jak uložit HTML soubor na Linuxu (nejjednodušší způsob)</strong></h1>
<h3 data-start="435" data-end="467"><strong data-start="439" data-end="467">1. Otevři textový editor</strong></h3>
<p data-start="468" data-end="483">Stačí kliknout:</p>
<ul data-start="485" data-end="577">
<li data-start="485" data-end="534">
<p data-start="487" data-end="534"><strong data-start="487" data-end="505">Ubuntu / GNOME</strong> → „Text Editor“ nebo „Gedit“</p>
</li>
<li data-start="535" data-end="553">
<p data-start="537" data-end="553"><strong data-start="537" data-end="544">KDE</strong> → „Kate“</p>
</li>
<li data-start="554" data-end="577">
<p data-start="556" data-end="577"><strong data-start="556" data-end="564">XFCE</strong> → „Mousepad“</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="579" data-end="602">Cokoliv z toho funguje.</p>
<hr data-start="604" data-end="607">
<h3 data-start="609" data-end="664"><strong data-start="613" data-end="664">2. Vlož text, který jsem ti poslal (index.html)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="665" data-end="703">Klikni dovnitř editoru → <strong data-start="690" data-end="702">Ctrl + V</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="705" data-end="708">
<h3 data-start="710" data-end="732"><strong data-start="714" data-end="732">3. Ulož soubor</strong></h3>
<p data-start="733" data-end="740">Jdi na:</p>
<p data-start="742" data-end="767"><strong data-start="742" data-end="767">Soubor → Uložit jako…</strong></p>
<p data-start="769" data-end="790">A teď nejdůležitější:</p>
<ul data-start="792" data-end="922">
<li data-start="792" data-end="817">
<p data-start="794" data-end="817">Název: <strong data-start="801" data-end="815">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="818" data-end="883">
<p data-start="820" data-end="883">Typ: <strong data-start="825" data-end="856">Všechny soubory / All files</strong> <em data-start="857" data-end="881">(pokud tam možnost je)</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="884" data-end="922">
<p data-start="886" data-end="922">Místo uložení: složka <strong data-start="908" data-end="922">washerlife</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="924" data-end="1033">💡 Pokud nevidíš volbu typu souboru → nevadí, Linux neudělá <code data-start="984" data-end="990">.txt</code> navíc.<br data-start="997" data-end="1000">
Stačí fakt napsat <strong data-start="1018" data-end="1032">index.html</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1035" data-end="1053">Klikni <strong data-start="1042" data-end="1052">Uložit</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1055" data-end="1058">
<h1 data-start="1060" data-end="1089">🧩 <strong data-start="1065" data-end="1089">4. Vytvoř CSS soubor</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1090" data-end="1110">Stejně jako předtím:</p>
<ol data-start="1112" data-end="1271">
<li data-start="1112" data-end="1151">
<p data-start="1115" data-end="1151">Otevři nový dokument (Soubor → Nový)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1152" data-end="1179">
<p data-start="1155" data-end="1179">Vlož text <strong data-start="1165" data-end="1179">styles.css</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1180" data-end="1204">
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1204">Soubor → Uložit jako…</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1205" data-end="1229">
<p data-start="1208" data-end="1229">Název: <strong data-start="1215" data-end="1229">styles.css</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1230" data-end="1271">
<p data-start="1233" data-end="1271">Uložit do stejné složky <strong data-start="1257" data-end="1271">washerlife</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1273" data-end="1280">Hotovo.</p>
<hr data-start="1282" data-end="1285">
<h1 data-start="1287" data-end="1327">🧩 <strong data-start="1292" data-end="1327">5. Zkontroluj, že se to povedlo</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1329" data-end="1366">Ve složce <code data-start="1339" data-end="1351">washerlife</code> bys měl vidět:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1368" data-end="1440"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span><br><span>styles.css</span><br><span>washerlife-hero.jpg   (ten přidáš později)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1442" data-end="1513">Žádné <code data-start="1448" data-end="1454">.txt</code>, žádné ikony textu se zeleným plus → jen obyčejné soubory.</p>
<hr data-start="1515" data-end="1518">
<h1 data-start="1520" data-end="1571">🧪 <strong data-start="1525" data-end="1571">6. Otevři index.html ve webovém prohlížeči</strong></h1>
<p data-start="1572" data-end="1582">Ve složce:</p>
<p data-start="1584" data-end="1636">👉 pravým tlačítkem → <strong data-start="1606" data-end="1636">Open with Firefox / Chrome</strong></p>
<p data-start="1638" data-end="1697">Když všechno funguje → uvidíš svůj Washer Life web lokálně.</p>
<hr data-start="1699" data-end="1702">
<h1 data-start="1704" data-end="1748">🟣 Pokud chceš TOTÁLNĚ bezbolestný postup:</h1>
<p data-start="1749" data-end="1805">Můžu ti připravit <strong data-start="1767" data-end="1774">ZIP</strong>, který jen stáhneš a rozbalíš.</p>
<p data-start="1807" data-end="1819">V ZIPu bude:</p>
<ul data-start="1821" data-end="1924">
<li data-start="1821" data-end="1836">
<p data-start="1823" data-end="1836"><code data-start="1823" data-end="1836">/index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1837" data-end="1852">
<p data-start="1839" data-end="1852"><code data-start="1839" data-end="1852">/styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1853" data-end="1884">
<p data-start="1855" data-end="1884"><code data-start="1855" data-end="1884">/assets/washerlife-hero.jpg</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1885" data-end="1924">
<p data-start="1887" data-end="1924">složka připravená pro GitHub a Vercel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1926" data-end="1975"><strong data-start="1926" data-end="1943">Stačí napsat:</strong><br data-start="1943" data-end="1946">
👉 <strong data-start="1949" data-end="1975">„Chci ZIP pro Vercel.“</strong></p>
<p data-start="1977" data-end="2026" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">A máš to bez ručního ukládání a bez rizika chyby.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-test