Tady máš svůj <strong data-start="27" data-end="73">ZIP balíček připravený pro GitHub + Vercel</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="76" data-end="142">👉 <strong data-start="79" data-end="142"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">Stáhnout washerlife.zip</button></span></strong></p>
<p data-start="144" data-end="158">V ZIPu najdeš:</p>
<ul data-start="160" data-end="271">
<li data-start="160" data-end="176">
<p data-start="162" data-end="176"><code data-start="162" data-end="174">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="177" data-end="193">
<p data-start="179" data-end="193"><code data-start="179" data-end="191">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="194" data-end="271">
<p data-start="196" data-end="271"><code data-start="196" data-end="217">washerlife-hero.jpg</code> (prázdný placeholder – vyměníš za skutečný obrázek)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="273" data-end="276">
<h2 data-start="278" data-end="301">📦 Co teď uděláš ty?</h2>
<ol data-start="303" data-end="489">
<li data-start="303" data-end="320">
<p data-start="306" data-end="320"><strong data-start="306" data-end="320">Stáhni ZIP</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="321" data-end="355">
<p data-start="324" data-end="355">Rozbal ho do složky na počítači</p>
</li>
<li data-start="356" data-end="399">
<p data-start="359" data-end="399">Nahraj obsah do nového GitHub repozitáře</p>
</li>
<li data-start="400" data-end="447">
<p data-start="403" data-end="447">Vercel → „New Project“ → vyber repo → Deploy</p>
</li>
<li data-start="448" data-end="489">
<p data-start="451" data-end="489">(Zítra) Přidáš doménu <code data-start="473" data-end="489">washerlife.com</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="491" data-end="494">
<p data-start="496" data-end="557">Pokud chceš, vytvořím <strong data-start="518" data-end="556">druhou verzi ZIPu s plným designem</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="559" data-end="711">
<li data-start="559" data-end="579">
<p data-start="561" data-end="579">kompletní layout</p>
</li>
<li data-start="580" data-end="602">
<p data-start="582" data-end="602">sekce Today’s Wash</p>
</li>
<li data-start="603" data-end="623">
<p data-start="605" data-end="623">produktové karty</p>
</li>
<li data-start="624" data-end="638">
<p data-start="626" data-end="638">story blok</p>
</li>
<li data-start="639" data-end="652">
<p data-start="641" data-end="652">final CTA</p>
</li>
<li data-start="653" data-end="680">
<p data-start="655" data-end="680">všechny stylované prvky</p>
</li>
<li data-start="681" data-end="711">
<p data-start="683" data-end="711">ready-for-vercel bez úprav</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="713" data-end="802" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Stačí říct:<br data-start="724" data-end="727">
