<h3 data-start="357" data-end="388"><strong data-start="361" data-end="388">Description (optional):</strong></h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="389" data-end="421"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Washer Life landing page</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="423" data-end="438">Visibility:</h3>
<ul data-start="439" data-end="483">
<li data-start="439" data-end="483">
<p data-start="441" data-end="483"><strong data-start="441" data-end="451">Public</strong> (doporučuji, můžeš sdílet link)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="485" data-end="506">Nic jiného nevyplňuj.</p>
<hr data-start="508" data-end="511">
<h1 data-start="513" data-end="551">✅ 3) Klikni na <strong data-start="530" data-end="551">Create repository</strong></h1>
<p data-start="553" data-end="589">Hotovo — vytvoří se ti prázdné repo.</p>
<hr data-start="591" data-end="594">
<h1 data-start="596" data-end="650">✅ 4) Nahraj ZIP soubory ručně (nejjednodušší způsob)</h1>
<p data-start="652" data-end="690">Po vytvoření repa uvidíš stránku typu:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="692" data-end="754"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Quick setup — if you’ve done this kind of thing before</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="756" data-end="778">A dole uvidíš možnost:</p>
<h3 data-start="780" data-end="813">➜ <strong data-start="786" data-end="813">Upload an existing file</strong></h3>
<p data-start="815" data-end="828">Klikni na to.</p>
<hr data-start="830" data-end="833">
<h1 data-start="835" data-end="859">✅ 5) Nahraj obsah ZIPu</h1>
<p data-start="861" data-end="930">Důležité: <strong data-start="871" data-end="877">NE</strong> nahrávej ZIP sám.<br data-start="895" data-end="898">
Musíš ZIP <strong data-start="908" data-end="920">rozbalit</strong> a nahrát:</p>
<ul data-start="932" data-end="985">
<li data-start="932" data-end="946">
<p data-start="934" data-end="946"><code data-start="934" data-end="946">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="947" data-end="961">
<p data-start="949" data-end="961"><code data-start="949" data-end="961">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="962" data-end="985">
<p data-start="964" data-end="985"><code data-start="964" data-end="985">washerlife-hero.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="987" data-end="993">Takže:</p>
<ol data-start="995" data-end="1125">
<li data-start="995" data-end="1047">
<p data-start="998" data-end="1047">Otevři na počítači složku, kde máš rozbalený ZIP.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1048" data-end="1088">
<p data-start="1051" data-end="1088">Přetáhni ty 3 soubory do GitHub okna.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1089" data-end="1125">
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1125">Klikni <strong data-start="1099" data-end="1117">Commit changes</strong> (dole).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1127" data-end="1156">Hotovo — tvoje repo existuje.</p>
<hr data-start="1158" data-end="1161">
<h1 data-start="1163" data-end="1206">🤖 Až to uděláš, dej mi sem link na repo:</h1>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1212">Např:</p>
