ata-turn-id="7932fd8c-e1fb-4238-adc8-07d5c47dcd1b" data-testid="conversation-turn-50" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="7932fd8c-e1fb-4238-adc8-07d5c47dcd1b" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="105">Perfektní! 🚀<br data-start="13" data-end="16">
Teď už jsi v úplně správné sekci — Vercel chce, aby sis vybral, odkud projekt importuješ.</p>
<p data-start="107" data-end="129">Uděláš jen 2 kliknutí:</p>
<hr data-start="131" data-end="134">
<h1 data-start="136" data-end="177">✅ 1) Klikni na <strong data-start="153" data-end="177">Continue with GitHub</strong></h1>
<p data-start="179" data-end="212">Je to ten <strong data-start="189" data-end="205">černý button</strong> vlevo:</p>
<p data-start="214" data-end="246"><strong data-start="214" data-end="238">Continue with GitHub</strong><br data-start="238" data-end="241">
⬛️ 🐱</p>
<hr data-start="248" data-end="251">
<h1 data-start="253" data-end="303">🟡 Možná tě to ještě vyzve k povolení přístupu</h1>
<p data-start="304" data-end="320">GitHub se zeptá:</p>
<p data-start="322" data-end="357">„Vercel chce přístup k vašim repo…“</p>
<p data-start="359" data-end="366">Klikni:</p>
<p data-start="368" data-end="465">👉 <strong data-start="371" data-end="384">Authorize</strong><br data-start="384" data-end="387">
👉 Vyber <strong data-start="396" data-end="424">Pouze vybrané repozitáře</strong> (doporučeno)<br data-start="437" data-end="440">
👉 A vyber <strong data-start="451" data-end="465">washerlife</strong></p>
<hr data-start="467" data-end="470">
<h1 data-start="472" data-end="517">✅ 2) Vercel načte seznam tvých repozitářů</h1>
<p data-start="518" data-end="576">Uvidíš tam <strong data-start="529" data-end="543">washerlife</strong> (ten, který jsi právě vytvořil).</p>
<p data-start="578" data-end="615">Klikni na <strong data-start="588" data-end="598">Import</strong> / <strong data-start="601" data-end="608">Add</strong> u něj.</p>
<hr data-start="617" data-end="620">
<h1 data-start="622" data-end="654">🟢 3) Vercel vytvoří projekt</h1>
<p data-start="655" data-end="680"><em data-start="655" data-end="660">Nic</em> nemusíš nastavovat.</p>
<p data-start="682" data-end="693">Jen klikni:</p>
<p data-start="695" data-end="708">👉 <strong data-start="698" data-end="708">Deploy</strong></p>
<hr data-start="710" data-end="713">
<h1 data-start="715" data-end="761">🎉 4) Vercel dokončí deploy (cca 5 sekund)</h1>
<p data-start="762" data-end="782">A zobrazí ti adresu:</p>
