<p data-start="86" data-end="186">👉 <strong data-start="89" data-end="142">Vercel ještě není přihlášený k tvému GitHub účtu.</strong><br data-start="142" data-end="145">
Musíme to ručně povolit jedním kliknutím.</p>
<p data-start="188" data-end="209">To spravíme okamžitě.</p>
<hr data-start="211" data-end="214">
<h1 data-start="216" data-end="268">🔧 KROK 1 → Klikni na <strong data-start="240" data-end="268">Manage Login Connections</strong></h1>
<p data-start="269" data-end="314">Je to malý text hned pod těmi třemi tlačítky:</p>
<p data-start="316" data-end="365"><strong data-start="316" data-end="344">Manage Login Connections</strong><br data-start="344" data-end="347">
(s ikonou šipky ↗)</p>
<p data-start="367" data-end="383">📌 Klikni na to.</p>
<hr data-start="385" data-end="388">
<h1 data-start="390" data-end="445">🔧 KROK 2 → Vercel otevře stránku s propojením účtů</h1>
<p data-start="446" data-end="471">Uvidíš panel s možnostmi:</p>
<ul data-start="473" data-end="502">
<li data-start="473" data-end="481">
<p data-start="475" data-end="481">GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="482" data-end="490">
<p data-start="484" data-end="490">GitLab</p>
</li>
<li data-start="491" data-end="502">
<p data-start="493" data-end="502">Bitbucket</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="504" data-end="549">GitHub bude „Not connected“ nebo „Reconnect“.</p>
<hr data-start="551" data-end="554">
<h1 data-start="556" data-end="600">🔧 KROK 3 → Klikni na <strong data-start="580" data-end="598">Connect GitHub</strong></h1>
<p data-start="601" data-end="640">Vyskočí GitHub okno „Authorize Vercel“.</p>
<p data-start="642" data-end="673">➡️ Klikni <strong data-start="652" data-end="672">Authorize Vercel</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="675" data-end="738">➡️ Vyber <strong data-start="684" data-end="712">Only select repositories</strong><br data-start="712" data-end="715">
➡️ Vyber <strong data-start="724" data-end="738">washerlife</strong></p>
<p data-start="740" data-end="747">Potvrď.</p>
<hr data-start="749" data-end="752">
<h1 data-start="754" data-end="799">🔧 KROK 4 → Vrať se zpět na „New Project“</h1>
<p data-start="800" data-end="806">A teď:</p>
<p data-start="808" data-end="866">👉 tlačítko <strong data-start="820" data-end="844">Continue with GitHub</strong> bude černé (aktivní).</p>
<p data-start="868" data-end="882">Klikni na něj.</p>
<hr data-start="884" data-end="887">
<h1 data-start="889" data-end="947">🔧 KROK 5 → V seznamu repozitářů uvidíš <strong data-start="931" data-end="945">washerlife</strong></h1>
<p data-start="948" data-end="979">Klikni <strong data-start="955" data-end="965">Import</strong> → <strong data-start="968" data-end="978">Deploy</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="981" data-end="984">
<h1 data-start="986" data-end="1044">🟢 Pokud chceš, můžeš mi poslat screenshot z kroků 1–2</h1>
