<p data-start="71" data-end="115"><strong data-start="71" data-end="115">GitHub – washerlife (Last used just now)</strong></p>
<p data-start="117" data-end="128">To znamená:</p>
<p data-start="130" data-end="213">👉 Vercel má přístup k tvému repozitáři<br data-start="169" data-end="172">
👉 Můžeš teď konečně deploynout projekt</p>
<p data-start="215" data-end="225">Jdeme dál:</p>
<hr data-start="227" data-end="230">
<h1 data-start="232" data-end="268">✅ 1) Vrať se zpět do „New Project“</h1>
<p data-start="269" data-end="292">Klikni vlevo v menu na:</p>
<h3 data-start="294" data-end="310"><strong data-start="298" data-end="310">Overview</strong></h3>
<p data-start="311" data-end="317">nebo</p>
<h3 data-start="318" data-end="335"><strong data-start="322" data-end="335">Dashboard</strong></h3>
<p data-start="337" data-end="343">A pak:</p>
<p data-start="345" data-end="399">👉 <strong data-start="348" data-end="369">Add New → Project</strong><br data-start="369" data-end="372">
(stejné místo jako předtím)</p>
<hr data-start="401" data-end="404">
<h1 data-start="406" data-end="463">✅ 2) Teď bude tlačítko <strong data-start="431" data-end="455">Continue with GitHub</strong> aktivní</h1>
<p data-start="464" data-end="478">Klikni na něj.</p>
<hr data-start="480" data-end="483">
<h1 data-start="485" data-end="528">✅ 3) Uvidíš seznam repozitářů z GitHubu</h1>
<p data-start="529" data-end="535">Najdi:</p>
<h3 data-start="537" data-end="555"><strong data-start="541" data-end="555">washerlife</strong></h3>
<p data-start="557" data-end="593">A klikni na <strong data-start="569" data-end="579">Import</strong> nebo <strong data-start="585" data-end="592">Add</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="595" data-end="598">
<h1 data-start="600" data-end="643">✅ 4) Vercel otevře stránku s nastavením</h1>
<p data-start="644" data-end="654">Nic neměň.</p>
<ul data-start="656" data-end="740">
<li data-start="656" data-end="687">
<p data-start="658" data-end="687">Framework: <strong data-start="669" data-end="685">Other / None</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="688" data-end="712">
<p data-start="690" data-end="712">Build Command: <strong data-start="705" data-end="710">–</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="713" data-end="740">
<p data-start="715" data-end="740">Output Directory: <strong data-start="733" data-end="738">/</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="742" data-end="749">Klikni:</p>
<h3 data-start="751" data-end="765"><strong data-start="755" data-end="765">Deploy</strong></h3>
<hr data-start="767" data-end="770">
<h1 data-start="772" data-end="816">🎉 5) Po pár sekundách bude stránka LIVE</h1>
<p data-start="817" data-end="833">Vercel ti ukáže:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="835" data-end="872"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" d