<h1 data-start="66" data-end="113">👉 <strong data-start="71" data-end="111">Musíš nainstalovat Vercel GitHub App</strong></h1>
<p data-start="114" data-end="158">(tím dovolíš Vercelu vidět tvoje repozitáře)</p>
<p data-start="160" data-end="198">Je to přesně ta černá ikona uprostřed:</p>
<h3 data-start="200" data-end="232"><strong data-start="204" data-end="232">🟪 Install (GitHub logo)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="234" data-end="256">Klikni na <strong data-start="244" data-end="255">Install</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="258" data-end="261">
<h1 data-start="263" data-end="289">Co se stane po kliknutí?</h1>
<p data-start="291" data-end="319">GitHub se otevře a zeptá se:</p>
<h3 data-start="321" data-end="356"><strong data-start="325" data-end="356">Install "Vercel" GitHub App</strong></h3>
<p data-start="358" data-end="375">A bude tam volba:</p>
<ul data-start="377" data-end="439">
<li data-start="377" data-end="408">
<p data-start="379" data-end="408"><strong data-start="379" data-end="399">All repositories</strong><br data-start="399" data-end="402">
nebo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="409" data-end="439">
<p data-start="411" data-end="439"><strong data-start="411" data-end="439">Only select repositories</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="441" data-end="447">Vyber:</p>
<p data-start="449" data-end="526">👉 <strong data-start="452" data-end="480">Only select repositories</strong><br data-start="480" data-end="483">
👉 Zaškrtni <strong data-start="495" data-end="509">washerlife</strong><br data-start="509" data-end="512">
👉 <strong data-start="515" data-end="526">Install</strong></p>
<p data-start="528" data-end="595">Tohle propojí GitHub repo → Vercel, aby Vercel <em data-start="575" data-end="582">viděl</em> že existuje.</p>
<hr data-start="597" data-end="600">
<h1 data-start="602" data-end="658">📌 Po instalaci se vrať zpátky do Vercel → New Project</h1>
<p data-start="659" data-end="665">A teď:</p>
<ul data-start="667" data-end="827">
<li data-start="667" data-end="745">
<p data-start="669" data-end="745">v poli „Select a Git Namespace“ vyber svůj GitHub účet (obvykle tvoje jméno)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="746" data-end="784">
<p data-start="748" data-end="784">v seznamu repo uvidíš <strong data-start="770" data-end="784">washerlife</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="785" data-end="807">
<p data-start="787" data-end="807">klikni na <strong data-start="797" data-end="807">Import</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="808" data-end="827">
<p data-start="810" data-end="827">klikni <strong data-start="817" data-end="827">Deploy</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="829" data-end="832">
