<hr data-start="417" data-end="420">
<h2 data-start="422" data-end="451">Co teď uděláš ty (3 kroky)</h2>
<ol data-start="453" data-end="757">
<li data-start="453" data-end="494">
<p data-start="456" data-end="494"><strong data-start="456" data-end="479">Stáhni a rozbal ZIP</strong> na počítači.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="495" data-end="699">
<p data-start="498" data-end="545">Jdi na GitHub do repa <code data-start="520" data-end="543">washerlife/washerlife</code></p>
<ul data-start="549" data-end="699">
<li data-start="549" data-end="587">
<p data-start="551" data-end="587">klikni <strong data-start="558" data-end="585">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
