<p data-start="593" data-end="663">nahraj <strong data-start="600" data-end="621">tyhle tři soubory</strong> a nech je <strong data-start="632" data-end="643">přepsat</strong> (overwrite) staré</p>
</li>
<li data-start="667" data-end="699">
<p data-start="669" data-end="699">dole klikni <strong data-start="681" data-end="699">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="700" data-end="757">
