<hr data-start="323" data-end="326">
<h1 data-start="328" data-end="358">✅ KROK 1: Otevři GitHub repo</h1>
<p data-start="359" data-end="370">Klikni sem:</p>
<p data-start="372" data-end="415">👉 <a data-start="375" data-end="415" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://github.com/washerlife/washerlife<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="417" data-end="453">(Ukaž mi screenshot, pokud jsi tam.)</p>
<hr data-start="455" data-end="458">
<h1 data-start="460" data-end="492">✅ KROK 2: Klikni na „Add file“</h1>
<p data-start="493" data-end="526">Vpravo nahoře je zelené tlačítko:</p>
<p data-start="528" data-end="563"><strong data-start="528" data-end="542">Add file ⏷</strong><br data-start="542" data-end="545">
→ <strong data-start="547" data-end="563">Upload files</strong></p>
