Máme to live.</p>
<p data-start="28" data-end="82">Když otevřeš<br data-start="40" data-end="43">
👉 <strong data-start="46" data-end="80"><a data-start="48" data-end="78" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://washerlife.vercel.app/">https://washerlife.vercel.app/<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
<p data-start="84" data-end="101">měl(a) bys vidět:</p>
<ul data-start="103" data-end="348">
<li data-start="103" data-end="143">
<p data-start="105" data-end="143">nahoře <strong data-start="112" data-end="127">WASHER LIFE</strong> v serif fontu</p>
</li>
<li data-start="144" data-end="223">
<p data-start="146" data-end="223">pod tím podtitul <em data-start="163" data-end="221">“Where cycles never end. Where socks disappear forever.”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="224" data-end="272">
<p data-start="226" data-end="272">uprostřed hero s pračkou (zatím placeholder)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="273" data-end="348">
<p data-start="275" data-end="348">sekce <strong data-start="281" data-end="297">Today’s Wash</strong>, <strong data-start="299" data-end="319">Pick your powder</strong>, <strong data-start="321" data-end="329">WHY?</strong>, tlačítka BUY atd.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="350" data-end="423">👉 Pokud pořád vidíš jen „Local test version…“, udělej <strong data-start="405" data-end="422">tvrdý refresh</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="425" data-end="492">
<li data-start="425" data-end="492">
<p data-start="427" data-end="492">v prohlížeči: <strong data-start="441" data-end="454">Ctrl + F5</strong> (nebo Shift + Reload)<br data-start="476" data-end="479">
a zkus znovu.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="494" data-end="497">
<h2 data-start="499" data-end="532">Co dál (teď ty, krok po kroku)</h2>
<ol data-start="534" data-end="1207">
<li data-start="534" data-end="597">
<p data-start="537" data-end="597"><strong data-start="537" data-end="567">Ověř, že vidíš nový design</strong><br data-start="567" data-end="570">
– po Ctrl+F5 by měl být.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="599" data-end="788">
<p data-start="602" data-end="653"><strong data-start="602" data-end="643">Až budeš mít lepší fotku svojí pračky</strong>, uděláme:</p>
<ul data-start="657" data-end="788">
<li data-start="657" data-end="749">
<p data-start="659" data-end="749">na GitHubu klikneš na <code data-start="681" data-end="702">washerlife-hero.jpg</code> → <strong data-start="705" data-end="716">Replace</strong> → nahrát nový obrázek → Commit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="753" data-end="788">
<p data-start="755" data-end="788">hotovo, Vercel se sám redeployne.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="790" data-end="960">
<p data-start="793" data-end="818"><strong data-start="793" data-end="816">Chceš změnit texty?</strong></p>
<ul data-start="822" data-end="960">
<li data-start="822" data-end="883">
<p data-start="824" data-end="883">v repu klikni na <code data-start="841" data-end="853">index.html</code> → vpravo nahoře <strong data-start="870" data-end="881">✏️ Edit</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="887" data-end="929">
<p data-start="889" data-end="929">uprav text (třeba dnešní wash message)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="933" data-end="960">
<p data-start="935" data-end="960">dole <strong data-start="940" data-end="958">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="962" data-end="1207">
<p data-start="965" data-end="1008"><strong data-start="965" data-end="1008">Zítra, až pojede doména washerlife.com:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1012" data-end="1207">
<li data-start="1012" data-end="1094">
<p data-start="1014" data-end="1094">Vercel → projekt <code data-start="1031" data-end="1043">washerlife</code> → vlevo <strong data-start="1052" data-end="1063">Domains</strong> → <strong data-start="1066" data-end="1073">Add</strong> → <code data-start="1076" data-end="1092">washerlife.com</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1098" data-end="1207">
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1207">Websupport → DNS zóna pro <code data-start="1126" data-end="1142">washerlife.com</code> → nasměruj na Vercel (napíšu ti přesně jak, až to bude aktuální)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1209" data-end="1212">
<p data-start="1214" data-end="1243">Jestli chceš, v dalším kroku:</p>
<ul data-start="1245" data-end="1485">
<li data-start="1245" data-end="1295">
<p data-start="1247" data-end="1295">přepíšu texty do <strong data-start="1264" data-end="1275">češtiny</strong> (cine + meme styl),</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1296" data-end="1384">
<p data-start="1298" data-end="1384">vymyslíme konkrétní <strong data-start="1318" data-end="1330">BUY flow</strong> (zatím mail, pak třeba jednoduchý „form objednávky“),</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1385" data-end="1485">
<p data-start="1387" data-end="1485">navrhnu ti, jak tam pak přidáš <strong data-start="1418" data-end="1441">reálné video pračky</strong> (YouTube embed místo „Video will go here“).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1487" data-end="1584" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Napiš mi jen:<br data-start="1500" data-end="1503">
👉 „Chci české texty“ nebo „Chci napojit BUY na mail / formulář“<br data-start="1567" data-end="1570">
a pokračujeme.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 