olute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: scale(0);"><div class="bg-token-text-primary h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip rtl:origin-top-right" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full flex-row items-start justify-between gap-4 text-start"><button class="flex min-w-0 shrink-1 gap-0.5 items-center"><span class="font-medium w-full"><span class="flex gap-1 text-start align-middle items-center truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary dark:text-[var(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)]" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="flex min-w-0 gap-1 items-center"><span class="min-w-0 truncate">Thought for 16s</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="01bde736-4ea0-4673-8334-f0aff29ad813" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="167">Dobře, tak to uděláme „jak to má být“ 😊<br data-start="40" data-end="43">
Připravil jsem ti <strong data-start="61" data-end="90">novou, mnohem hezčí verzi</strong> – cine + meme, s papírovými kartičkami, tape, pinama, glow kolem pračky atd.</p>
<h3 data-start="169" data-end="192">1️⃣ Stáhni nový ZIP</h3>
<p data-start="194" data-end="276">👉 <strong data-start="197" data-end="276"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">Stáhnout washerlife-full-v2.zip</button></span></strong></p>
<p data-start="278" data-end="289">V něm jsou:</p>
<ul data-start="291" data-end="485">
<li data-start="291" data-end="349">
<p data-start="293" data-end="349"><code data-start="293" data-end="305">index.html</code> – kompletní cinematic + meme landing page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="350" data-end="408">
<p data-start="352" data-end="408"><code data-start="352" data-end="364">styles.css</code> – nový design (papír, stíny, glow, tagy…)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="409" data-end="485">
<p data-start="411" data-end="485"><code data-start="411" data-end="432">washerlife-hero.jpg</code> – jen placeholder (pak nahradíš fotkou svojí pračky)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="487" data-end="490">
<h3 data-start="492" data-end="542">2️⃣ Nahraj to do GitHubu (stejně jako předtím)</h3>
<ol data-start="544" data-end="869">
<li data-start="544" data-end="608">
<p data-start="547" data-end="608">Jdi do repa:<br data-start="559" data-end="562">
👉 <a data-start="568" data-end="608" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://github.com/washerlife/washerlife<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="610" data-end="647">
<p data-start="613" data-end="647">Klikni <strong data-start="620" data-end="647">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="649" data-end="833">
<p data-start="652" data-end="689">Nahraj z toho ZIPu tyhle tři soubory:</p>
<ul data-start="694" data-end="757">
<li data-start="694" data-end="710">
<p data-start="696" data-end="710"><code data-start="696" data-end="708">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="714" data-end="730">
<p data-start="716" data-end="730"><code data-start="716" data-end="728">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="734" data-end="757">
<p data-start="736" data-end="757"><code data-start="736" data-end="757">washerlife-hero.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="762" data-end="833">(klidně je přetáhni myší, opět se <strong data-start="796" data-end="808">přepíšou</strong> staré verze – to chceme)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="835" data-end="869">
<p data-start="838" data-end="869">Dole klikni <strong data-start="850" data-end="868">Commit changes</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="871" data-end="874">
<h3 data-start="876" data-end="898">3️⃣ Zkontroluj web</h3>
<p data-start="900" data-end="986">Otevři znovu:<br data-start="913" data-end="916">
👉 <a data-start="919" data-end="949" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://washerlife.vercel.app/">https://washerlife.vercel.app/<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a><br data-start="949" data-end="952">
a dej <strong data-start="958" data-end="969">Ctrl+F5</strong> (tvrdý refresh).</p>
<p data-start="988" data-end="1014">Teď už by to mělo vypadat:</p>
<ul data-start="1016" data-end="1428">
<li data-start="1016" data-end="1107">
<p data-start="1018" data-end="1107">nahoře velký hero blok s kartičkou „Today’s wash message“ a tlačítkem <strong data-start="1088" data-end="1105">BUY DETERGENT</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1108" data-end="1183">
<p data-start="1110" data-end="1183">vedle toho kartička s pračkou, glow, tagy „Real washer / Fake serenity“</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1184" data-end="1266">
<p data-start="1186" data-end="1266">sekce <em data-start="1192" data-end="1206">Today’s Wash</em> s bílým „papírem“ připnutým pinem a videokartičkou s tape</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1267" data-end="1321">
<p data-start="1269" data-end="1321"><em data-start="1269" data-end="1287">Pick your powder</em> se dvěma sáčky a stíny pod nimi</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1322" data-end="1370">
<p data-start="1324" data-end="1370"><em data-start="1324" data-end="1331">Story</em> s další papírovou kartičkou a fotkou</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1371" data-end="1428">
<p data-start="1373" data-end="1428">dole velké <strong data-start="1384" data-end="1392">WHY?</strong> a tlačítko „BUY SOAP &amp; ACCEPT FATE“</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1430" data-end="1433">
<p data-start="1435" data-end="1596" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Až to nahráš a refreshneš, pošli prosím screen z webu – když se ti něco nebude líbit (barvy, text, spacing), doladíme to. <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Coding Citation" class="rounded-xl px-1 text-token-text-secondary bg-token-bg-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-interactive-bg-secondary-selected"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-lab