Vercel neumí použít ZIP uvnitř repozitáře.<br data-start="73" data-end="76">
Musíš nahrát <strong data-start="89" data-end="124">obsah ZIPu – jednotlivé soubory</strong>, ne ZIP jako soubor.</p>
<p data-start="147" data-end="184">Proto se ti nezobrazila moje grafika.</p>
<hr data-start="186" data-end="189">
<h1 data-start="191" data-end="227">👉 Co musíš udělat teď (2 minuty):</h1>
<h3 data-start="229" data-end="255">1️⃣ Klikni na soubor</h3>
<p data-start="256" data-end="284"><code data-start="256" data-end="284">washerlife-full-v2 (2).zip</code></p>
<h3 data-start="286" data-end="329">2️⃣ Vpravo klikni na <strong data-start="311" data-end="321">Delete</strong> / 🗑️</h3>
<p data-start="330" data-end="341">A ZIP smaž.</p>
<hr data-start="343" data-end="346">
<h1 data-start="348" data-end="387">3️⃣ Rozbal ten ZIP u sebe na počítači</h1>
<p data-start="389" data-end="425">V ZIPu jsou složky a soubory, např.:</p>
<ul data-start="427" data-end="509">
<li data-start="427" data-end="441">
<p data-start="429" data-end="441"><code data-start="429" data-end="441">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="442" data-end="456">
<p data-start="444" data-end="456"><code data-start="444" data-end="456">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="457" data-end="470">
<p data-start="459" data-end="470"><code data-start="459" data-end="470">script.js</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="471" data-end="491">
<p data-start="473" data-end="491"><code data-start="473" data-end="482">assets/</code> (složka)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="492" data-end="509">
<p data-start="494" data-end="509"><code data-start="494" data-end="504">hero.png</code> atd.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="511" data-end="514">
<h1 data-start="516" data-end="560">4️⃣ Nahraj VŠECHNY tyto soubory do GitHubu</h1>
<p data-start="562" data-end="572">V GitHubu:</p>
<p data-start="574" data-end="692">➡️ <strong data-start="577" data-end="604">Add file → Upload files</strong><br data-start="604" data-end="607">
➡️ Přetáhni <strong data-start="619" data-end="650">celý obsah rozbaleného ZIPu</strong> (NE samotný ZIP!)<br data-start="668" data-end="671">
➡️ <strong data-start="674" data-end="692">Commit changes</strong></p>
<hr data-start="694" data-end="697">
<h1 data-start="699" data-end="773">🔥 Po commitu Vercel udělá nový deploy a web bude 1:1 jako moje grafika.</h1>
