<hr data-start="258" data-end="261">
<h3 data-start="263" data-end="284">✔ Co ZIP obsahuje</h3>
<p data-start="286" data-end="321">Tento balík je připravený tak, aby:</p>
<ul data-start="323" data-end="453">
<li data-start="323" data-end="346">
<p data-start="325" data-end="346">šel normálně rozbalit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="347" data-end="399">
<p data-start="349" data-end="399">měl kompletní strukturu projektu (složky, soubory)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="400" data-end="453">
<p data-start="402" data-end="453">fungoval jako základ pro nahrání na GitHub + Vercel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="455" data-end="476"><strong data-start="455" data-end="476">Struktura uvnitř:</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="478" data-end="642"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>washerlife-full-final/</span><br><span>├── index.html</span><br><span>├── styles.css</span><br><span>├── img/</span><br><span>│   └── placeholder.txt</span><br><span>├── assets/</span><br><span>│   └── placeholder.txt</span><br><span>└── fonts/</span><br><span>    └── placeholder.txt</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="644" data-end="767"><strong data-start="644" data-end="654">POZOR:</strong> Všechny placeholdery jsou jen „držáky“ pro strukturu – skutečná grafika přijde až potom (tu ti vygeneruju taky).</p>
<hr data-start="769" data-end="772">
<h3 data-start="774" data-end="794">✔ Co teď uděláš?</h3>
<p data-start="796" data-end="941">1️⃣ <strong data-start="800" data-end="814">ZIP stáhni</strong><br data-start="814" data-end="817">
2️⃣ <strong data-start="821" data-end="852">Rozbal ho normálně v Linuxu</strong><br data-start="852" data-end="855">
3️⃣ Na GitHubu klikni:<br data-start="877" data-end="880">
<strong data-start="883" data-end="941">Add file → Upload files → Vyber obsah složky (ne ZIP!)</strong></p>
<p data-start="943" data-end="993">NEZIPUJ znova – nahrává se obsah rozbalené složky.</p>
<hr data-start="995" data-end="998">
<p data-start="1000" data-end="1044">Až to tam bude → napíšeš <em data-start="1025" data-end="1035">„hotovo“</em> → já ti:</p>
<h3 data-start="1046" data-end="1127">🔥 Nahraju kompletní grafiku a finální HTML/CSS design (ten krásný, co chceš)</h3>
