Teď ještě musíme přemluvit prohlížeč, aby načetl <strong data-start="75" data-end="90">novou verzi</strong> a ne nějakou starou z cache.</p>
<h2 data-start="121" data-end="150">1️⃣ Udělej „tvrdý refresh“</h2>
<p data-start="152" data-end="196">Na stránce <code data-start="163" data-end="195">https://washerlife.vercel.app/</code>:</p>
<ul data-start="198" data-end="293">
<li data-start="198" data-end="228">
<p data-start="200" data-end="228">na <strong data-start="203" data-end="213">Linuxu</strong>: <code data-start="215" data-end="226">Ctrl + F5</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="229" data-end="260">
<p data-start="231" data-end="260">na <strong data-start="234" data-end="245">Windows</strong>: <code data-start="247" data-end="258">Ctrl + F5</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="261" data-end="293">
<p data-start="263" data-end="293">na <strong data-start="266" data-end="274">Macu</strong>: <code data-start="276" data-end="293">Cmd + Shift + R</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="295" data-end="343">Nebo to otevři v <strong data-start="312" data-end="337">anonymním / incognito</strong> okně.</p>
<hr data-start="345" data-end="348">
<h2 data-start="350" data-end="382">2️⃣ Co bys tam TEĎ měla vidět</h2>
<p data-start="384" data-end="417">Podle kódu, který máš na GitHubu:</p>
<ul data-start="419" data-end="804">
<li data-start="419" data-end="459">
<p data-start="421" data-end="459">jemné béžovo-modré pozadí (gradient)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="460" data-end="548">
<p data-start="462" data-end="548">nahoře lištu s logem <strong data-start="483" data-end="498">WASHER LIFE</strong> a odkazy „Today’s Wash / Powders / Story / BUY“</p>
</li>
<li data-start="549" data-end="633">
<p data-start="551" data-end="633">velký hero blok s textem „WASHER LIFE“ + popisek (kde ponožky mizí navždy apod.)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="634" data-end="695">
<p data-start="636" data-end="695">pod tím sekce „Today’s Wash“ s kartičkou a vedle videobox</p>
</li>
<li data-start="696" data-end="746">
<p data-start="698" data-end="746">sekci s dvěma prášky (White Wash / Color Wash)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="747" data-end="804">
<p data-start="749" data-end="804">dole „Why? We don’t know. But it spins.“ + tlačítko BUY</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="806" data-end="845">To je ta moje cine + meme landing page.</p>
<hr data-start="847" data-end="850">
<h2 data-start="852" data-end="908">3️⃣ Jestli tam <em data-start="870" data-end="890">po tvrdém refreshi</em> vidíš něco jiného</h2>
<p data-start="910" data-end="917">Prosím:</p>
<ol data-start="919" data-end="1004">
<li data-start="919" data-end="987">
<p data-start="922" data-end="987">udělej <strong data-start="929" data-end="956">screenshot celé stránky</strong> (jako jsi dělala z GitHubu),</p>
</li>
<li data-start="988" data-end="1004">
<p data-start="991" data-end="1004">pošli ho sem.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1006" data-end="1051">Podle obrázku hned poznám, jestli je problém:</p>
<ul data-start="1053" data-end="1188">
<li data-start="1053" data-end="1083">
<p data-start="1055" data-end="1083">jen v cachi (browser, CDN)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1084" data-end="1188">
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1188">nebo jestli Vercel pořád servíruje starší deploy a budeme muset jeden klik udělat přímo v Deployments.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1319" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Ale podle toho, že HTML i CSS máš fakt správné, jsme už úplně v cílové rovince – teď je to jen o tom, co ti prohlížeč podstrkuje.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-b