t="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="d1831a16-d97c-47ef-979b-8452f76b516d" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="179">Super, teď už to vypadá parádně – jen ta pračka dělá, že neexistuje 😄<br data-start="70" data-end="73">
To bílé okno s textem <em data-start="95" data-end="126">“Washer Life washing machine”</em> znamená: <strong data-start="136" data-end="179">HTML obrázek hledá, ale nenajde soubor.</strong></p>
<p data-start="181" data-end="210">Takže máme jen 3 možné chyby:</p>
<ol data-start="212" data-end="374">
<li data-start="212" data-end="250">
<p data-start="215" data-end="250">jiný název souboru / jiná přípona</p>
</li>
<li data-start="251" data-end="317">
<p data-start="254" data-end="317">jiná cesta (např. v HTML je <code data-start="282" data-end="289">img/…</code>, ale soubor leží v rootu)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="318" data-end="374">
<p data-start="321" data-end="374">velká/malá písmena (Linux/ Vercel jsou na to hákliví)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="376" data-end="379">
<h2 data-start="381" data-end="430">1️⃣ Ověř, že soubor na webu <em data-start="412" data-end="430">opravdu existuje</em></h2>
<p data-start="432" data-end="464">Do prohlížeče zkus ručně napsat:</p>
<blockquote data-start="466" data-end="519">
<p data-start="468" data-end="519"><code data-start="468" data-end="519">https://washerlife.vercel.app/washerlife-hero.jpg</code></p>
</blockquote>
<ul data-start="521" data-end="656">
<li data-start="521" data-end="591">
<p data-start="523" data-end="591">Pokud se otevře fotka → soubor je OK a je jen špatně zapsaný v HTML.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="592" data-end="656">
<p data-start="594" data-end="656">Pokud 404 / nic → Vercel ten soubor nemá (nebo má jiný název).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="658" data-end="661">
<h2 data-start="663" data-end="708">2️⃣ Zkontrolujeme název souboru na GitHubu</h2>
<p data-start="710" data-end="754">Na GitHubu v repu <code data-start="728" data-end="753">washerlife / washerlife</code>:</p>
<ol data-start="756" data-end="1032">
<li data-start="756" data-end="797">
<p data-start="759" data-end="797">Jdi na záložku <strong data-start="774" data-end="782">Code</strong> (to už máš).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="798" data-end="1032">
<p data-start="801" data-end="869">V levém seznamu souborů se podívej na třetí soubor – přesný název:</p>
<p data-start="874" data-end="895">Měl by být něco jako:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="900" data-end="937"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Plain text</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>washerlife-hero.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="942" data-end="1032">Zapiš si ho <strong data-start="954" data-end="964">přesně</strong> (včetně velkých/malých písmen a přípony <code data-start="1005" data-end="1011">.jpg</code> / <code data-start="1014" data-end="1021">.jpeg</code> / <code data-start="1024" data-end="1030">.png</code>).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1034" data-end="1037">
<h2 data-start="1039" data-end="1081">3️⃣ Zkontrolujeme HTML řádek s obrázkem</h2>
<ol data-start="1083" data-end="1168">
<li data-start="1083" data-end="1118">
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1118">Vlevo klikni na <strong data-start="1102" data-end="1116">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1119" data-end="1168">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1168">Klikni na ikonku tužky <strong data-start="1145" data-end="1163">Edit this file</strong> (🖊)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1170" data-end="1205">Najdi řádek s obrázkem (něco jako):</p>
