Napíšu ti <strong data-start="91" data-end="123">přesný postup krok za krokem</strong>, jako kdybys to dělala poprvé.</p>
<hr data-start="158" data-end="192">
<h1 data-start="194" data-end="253">✅ KROK 1 — Stáhni si obrázek pračky (znovu ti ho nahraju)</h1>
<p data-start="255" data-end="362">Tady je nový obrázek v ZIPu – <em data-start="285" data-end="321">už rozbalený přímo jako soubor JPG</em>, takže ti půjde hned stáhnout kliknutím:</p>
<p data-start="364" data-end="408">👇 <strong data-start="367" data-end="408">Klikni pravým → Save as / Uložit jako</strong></p>
<p data-start="410" data-end="518">🔗 <strong data-start="413" data-end="433">STAŽENÍ SOUBORU:</strong><br data-start="433" data-end="436">
<a data-start="436" data-end="471" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://files.catbox.moe/uyh2xw.jpg<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a><br data-start="471" data-end="474">
<em data-start="474" data-end="518">(soubor se jmenuje: <code data-start="495" data-end="516">washerlife-hero.jpg</code>)</em></p>
<p data-start="520" data-end="550">📌 Ulož si ho např. na plochu.</p>
<hr data-start="552" data-end="586">
<h1 data-start="588" data-end="626">✅ KROK 2 — Nahraj obrázek do GitHubu</h1>
<ol data-start="628" data-end="831">
<li data-start="628" data-end="685">
<p data-start="631" data-end="685">Jdi sem:<br data-start="639" data-end="642">
<a data-start="645" data-end="685" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://github.com/washerlife/washerlife<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="686" data-end="732">
<p data-start="689" data-end="732">Vlevo klikni na <strong data-start="705" data-end="732">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="733" data-end="794">
<p data-start="736" data-end="794">Přetáhni soubor <strong data-start="752" data-end="775">washerlife-hero.jpg</strong> (který sis stáhla)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="795" data-end="831">
<p data-start="798" data-end="831">Dole klikni na <strong data-start="813" data-end="831">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="833" data-end="874">👉 Po nahrání musí být v seznamu souborů:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="876" data-end="925"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Code</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span><br><span>styles.css</span><br><span>washerlife-hero.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="927" data-end="961">
<h1 data-start="963" data-end="1017">✅ KROK 3 — Otevři index.html a nastav správnou cestu</h1>
<ol data-start="1019" data-end="1140">
<li data-start="1019" data-end="1048">
<p data-start="1022" data-end="1048">Klikni na <strong data-start="1032" data-end="1046">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1049" data-end="1093">
<p data-start="1052" data-end="1093">Klikni na ikonku tužky (Edit this file)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1094" data-end="1140">
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1140">Najdi řádek s obrázkem – bude nějak takhle:</p>
